messages.message:
Hi all :wave:! We are planning on organizing a bi-weekly internal Tech Talk series where we deep dive into various parts of the product from an engineering perspective. The goal is to provide a forum for technical knowledge sharing and discussion within IB Eng. These will be taking place on the alternating weeks without Demo Day.
For the very first talk, @Erick will be diving into *how Refiner works under the hood* :refiner:. Please tune in on *Feb 25th at 8:30am PST*!
If you have any thoughts/suggestions or want to volunteer to give a talk, please reach out to me!
this is great - will help on crossfunctional projects!
